---
title: Spicy Prawn Thai Coconut Soup with mushrooms, carrot and cashews
description: Red Thai curry paste is usually made up of chilli peppers, garlic and lemongrass among other things. It's one of the spicier types of Thai curry, but luckily in this soup, it's tempered with cooling coconut milk and paired with prawns for a beautifully balanced dish.
